How to create distribution source:

cvs export -r RELEASE-1_3_2 jade
mv jade openjade-1.3.2
cd openjade-1.3.2/docsrc
make
make clean
mv releasenotes.pdf releasenotes.html releasenotes.ps ..
cd ../config
autoconf
mv configure ..
rm -rf autom4te.cache
cd ../..
rm openjade-1.3.2/RELEASE
rm -rf openjade-1.3.2/lib
rm -rf openjade-1.3.2/nsgmls
rm -rf openjade-1.3.2/sgmlnorm
rm -rf openjade-1.3.2/spam
rm -rf openjade-1.3.2/spent
rm -rf openjade-1.3.2/sx
tar zcvf openjade-1.3.2.tar.gz openjade-1.3.2

Do something similar for Windows (i.e. checkout on Windows platform
so that CR/LF mapping is done correctly)
